<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Dec1938"><font color="red">28 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  Thank you for your three letters to Mr de la Mare &hellip; away till Monday (2 January 1939) &hellip; on his return he will deal with &hellip; the colour of the binding. The corrected galleys I have sent on to the printers straight away (Section 2 of Part III). </div>
